{"tid":458020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"D Mk以為有少少腹肌就好撚好打","createTime":"2017-11-04T12:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T12:42:36.000Z","uid":20352,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9ab9aa3c30384cc0cbcd613bc965bf953daf2c","tid":458020,"uid":20352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"05a7d3253d0983b62896516a8bd2611111f3c358","tid":458020,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"睇到厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9362f1d2b704ee206138dac8800abc505de062c6","tid":458020,"uid":81848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"十年前嘅潮文"},{"pid":"3befe8b72ac6ce25e907db95e2b5477191b1a868","tid":458020,"uid":17322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}